{"tid":998361,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"拍緊拖嘅你 信任呢家野要重修真係好撚難","createTime":"2019-01-28T02:12:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-28T04:34:11.000Z","uid":172390,"like":35,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"21f979d10c7dc9fbb8aa07da6abfa177d06b574f","tid":998361,"uid":172390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T02:12:41.000Z","msg":"奉勸各位拍緊拖嘅 真係唔好嘗試呃另一半<br />\n呃得一次就有第二次 但遲早有一日對方會知<br />\n如果你仲覺得你另一半係重要過你個大話<br />\n咁就唔好講大話<br />\n一段關係應該建立係信任之上<br />\n但你要親手破壞佢<br />\n如果對方依然包容係你好彩<br />\n但心入面點都會有條刺<br />\n唔好彩嘅你就執定野走啦<br />\n<br />\n所以真係唔好諗住呃對方或者暪住對方<br />\n否則比人揭穿個下 盞自己攞黎柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2fd9f931a57da9e4323bb0bf93ef4edacd36e9e5","tid":998361,"uid":105102,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T03:00:02.000Z","msg":"「呃你係唔想你唔開心」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b84cbe09d103905bba545d8a80d1f2de1a6c402f","tid":998361,"uid":38172,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T03:01:38.000Z","msg":"不應講的死也不說是否等於欺騙<br />\n衷心的欺騙 我真心想你快活如蜜甜<br />\n<br />\n有D野暪到一世係好事..."},{"pid":"98de99996e4b6bd2a9e3e70e807c5d3bb1071685","tid":998361,"uid":101557,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T03:09:21.000Z","msg":"善意嘅大話都唔可以講"},{"pid":"821e8c0cda80fcad6388894b892b12e9628793d6","tid":998361,"uid":32359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T03:13:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a53f42ab57f7a78cfebfb40bff72adb4481cd1e0","tid":998361,"uid":7355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T03:37:09.000Z","msg":"幾時都話 若要人不知 唔好咁低b"},{"pid":"df890d6d5b193b5c012f1d0ba06fd6a478a564ec","tid":998361,"uid":172390,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"2fd9f931a57da9e4323bb0bf93ef4edacd36e9e5","tid":998361,"uid":105102,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T03:00:02.000Z","msg":"「呃你係唔想你唔開心」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T04:34:11.000Z","msg":"咁講係為左自己個心好過啲<br />\n合理化自己做嘅野<br />\n但其實都係一樣咁仆街<br />\n如果你做啲野唔係唔比得人知<br />\n點解要講大話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}